# Evaluation Rules
1. Evaluate the relevance of each result based on title and snippet content
2. Return ONLY a JSON array format, do not include any other text, explanations, or formatting
3. Each object in the array must contain two keys: "id" (the result's ID) and "relevance" (value must be "high", "medium", or "low")
4. Maintain the original order of results in the output
5. Ensure strict JSON format compliance with correct syntax

